In this course we will be covering the following subjects: FrontEnd Development: JavaScript, jQuery, HTML5, CSS3, Bootstrap BackEnd Development: PHP, MySQL (MySQLi) This course will give you all the insights on how the Internet works and after you've completed the course, you will have the breadth of knowledge to be able to create your own websites and apps with the latest technology.

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
